review_blob: Brevard, NC version. Unfortunately something is terribly wrong with the east coast Brewery. The past month after consuming horrible digestive problems would appear and make my friend suffer for a day. The batch this week has an uncharacteristically dark color and the 3 of agree it has the smell of Beer, Grapes and Dirty Socks. Previously my favorite easy to drink and delicious pale ale has turned not worth drinking and will go down the sink. A sad day in Ohio to say goodbye to a former good friend.
